data.description:
Motivated Seller! All offers considered. 
Find your dream oasis here! Nestled in Lighthouse Hill Estates and close to Eagle Mountain Lake, this home has all of the extras. Upon entering the stately front door you will find the home office with cathedral windows. Continue on to the main living area with a tray ceiling and wood like tile then on to the eat in dining area. See the kitchen with gorgeous knotty alder cabinets, island, and lots of great counter space. The spacious laundry room has a sink, cabinets, and access to the master closet. The master bedroom with an en suite and closet straight off your life goals list. There are three additional bedrooms and one full bath. To finish off your entertaining check list, there is a half bath and a large secondary living room with access to the back porch. Sit by the fireplace on a chilly night or host a great outdoor party on this amazing patio. Make it yours in time for the cozy months.
